column5: Glad your weekend go saved Cliff.  Looks like dinner was good  Getting some practice for Lakair I see  Joey
Oh man.....I hope you washed the curse off that thing!!! Your more than welcome to join me anytime bud, you've got my number!!  Did you pick up one of those lucky spinner baits yet  Sinker
I'll grab some, but I'm going to try a few different things before I slap one on. And yeah, the curse is gone.
